description:
&lt;p&gt;Ramsay Health Care UK is one of the leading providers of NHS and private patient services in England, with a network of over 30 acute hospitals and Treatment Centres. Renacres Hospital is a private hospital set in pleasant grounds. It consists of two operating theatres and an Endoscopy/ Ambulatory unit which performs a large variety of surgery, orthopaedics being one our main areas. It is supported by full diagnostic services CT, MRI and X-ray and Physiotherapy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Details of the position&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for experienced, flexible and highly motivated qualified Theatre Practitioner/Scrub Nurseto join our multi skilled friendly Theatre Team, reporting to the Theatre Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Key responsibilities include:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In addition to your strong Clinical Skills you will possess:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The personality to work as part of a small dedicated team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The capacity to plan equipment and consumable requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team Leadership Skills an advantage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to participate in on call rota.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working to tight deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Applicant must be qualified to RGN level 1 or ODP and have proven post registration experience to include all aspects of Recovery, Scrub / Nursing across avariety of specialties.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;In return we offer:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary Plus Enhancements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;33 days annual leave inc bank holidays which increase with service (pro rata)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private Healthcare&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributory Pension Scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Life Assurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent Training and Development Opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Subsidised Staff Restaurant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free On Site Parking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All offers of employment will be subject to receipt of a satisfactory Enhanced Disclosure Certificate from the Disclosure and Barring Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Renacres Hospital is committed to quality, equality and opportunity for all.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
